headline: Could This Bull Market Buy Help You Become a Millionaire?
summary: If you're looking for a consumer stock that could be a millionaire maker, one of the top stocks to consider is Celsius Holdings (NASDAQ: CELH).  The reason why is quite simple -- rival Monster Beverage turned out to be one of the best-performing stocks over the past three decades.  With Celsius having a tough year in an otherwise strong market, could this be an opportunity to jump into a stock with a lot of long-term potential?
